border asked for help from soviet interior ministry troops after 
an aug 18 autonomy declaration by the gagauz who number about 
150000 
after the presidents speech sunday moldavias parliament 
passed a resolution ordering all militias moldavians russians 
ukrainians and gagauz to disband within 24 hours some units have 
reportedly armed themselves 
