what type of rights do they want i am not the one to be 
investigated i tell you if anyone wants to enjoy the human 
rights they have in the us in england and india provided that 
country accepts i will permit them to leave 
saw maungs latest crackdown has been against the buddhist 
clergy who had protested alleged killings by soldiers in early 
august 
on wednesday he banned unauthorized monks groups and 
threatened dissident offenders with up to three years in prison 
