in employment act of 1967 adea depending on how the high court 
rules in a decision expected by july suing under the act could 
become a bit easier or a bit more difficult 
stevens was employed at the irs austin service center for 19 
months before being promoted for a probationary period to a 
betterpaying job in 1986 but in the spring of 1987 during the 
probationary period he was returned to his old job 
