reporter bill moushey seeks 20000 in damages 
it said an article published in july 1989 would have caused 
readers to believe that ashton improperly helped justice rolf 
larsen buy property for less than it was worth and that larsen in 
turn asked another judge to give favorable treatment to one of 
ashtons cients 
the suit says ashton acted properly and the postgazette 
articles were false 
