johnny cash aretha franklin billy joel 
and quincy jones who share a total of 46 grammy awards among them 
will receive the 1990 grammy legends awards from the national 
academy of recording arts and sciences inc 
the awards will be given during the second annual grammy legends 
tribute a twohour primetime cbstv special for broadcast later 
this year the event will be taped before a live audience in new 
york on dec 5 
the grammy legends awards honors an artists ongoing creative 
contributions and influence in the recording fields 
equals 
new york ap one of new yorks most popular holiday 
traditions the christmas spectacular returns to radio city 
music hall on nov 9 
the 1990 version of this live musical extravaganza starring the 
rockettes features new production numbers original costumes and 
choreography director and choreographer scott salmon has created 
two new numbers for productions that star the rockettes we need 
a little christmas and the carol of the bells 
the christmas show at radio city premiered in 1933 tickets for 
the 1990 christmas spectaculer are priced at 3427 
equals 
new york ap the organization of asian women and the soho 20 
gallery will present an art auction of works by asian artists 
including martin wong yung soon min arlen huang and helen oji 
a benefit for the new york asian womens center will be held on 
dec 14 at the soho 20 gallery the center founded in 1982 is the 
first project on the east coast to address the problem of battering 
in asian communities 
the center provides a multilingual hotline counseling for 
battered women advocacy and a safe homes network it also provides 
community education regarding the economic and cultural realities 
faced by asian battered women 
equals 
los angeles ap the 8th annual american cinema awards an 
allstar salute to tom cruise james stewart lauren bacall and 
whitney houston will be held at the beverly hilton hotel on jan 
12 
the american cinema awards foundation will welcome over 300 
stars from the film television and recording fields the highlight 
of the evening will be tributes to stewart and bacall for 
distinguished achievement in film and to houston as the musical 
performer of the year 
this year a new award for film achievement will be given to an 
actor or actress who has made a major impact on the motion picture 
industry in the past decade the first recipient of this award will 
be tom cruise 
hosted by robert wagner for the past five years proceeds from 
the american cinama awards will benefit the motion picture and 
television country house and hospital in woodland hills calif 
establish ongoing scholarships in the fields of theater arts dance 
and music and provide free screenings for senior citizens and the 
disabled in hospitals throughout the united states 
